{"tid":2345472,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"讓我為你們祈禱","createTime":"2020-12-29T13:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T15:23:17.000Z","uid":344609,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54f37ca95171f0696e31f10e5080ea6d9885311f","tid":2345472,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>1 Corinthians 13:4-8</strong><br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"large\"><em>Love is patient, <br />\nlove is kind. <br />\nIt does not envy, <br />\nit does not boast, <br />\nit is not proud. <br />\nIt does not dishonor others, <br />\nit is not self-seeking, <br />\nit is not easily angered, <br />\nit keeps no record of wrongs. <br />\nLove does not delight in evil but<br />\n rejoices with the truth. <br />\nIt always protects, always trusts, <br />\nalways hopes, always perseveres. <br />\nLove never fails.</em></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太陽啊月亮啊 <br />\n請您們隨着新的一年讓世上所有受苦的人（除了邪惡的人）都能勇敢去愛和被愛。<br />\n<br />\n請您們在新的一年祝福所有人（除了邪惡的人）能早些找到自己的幸福。<br />\n<br />\n願世上所有小朋友都能夠有快樂的童年。<br />\n<br />\n請您們保佑在遠處的12位門徒。<br />\n<br />\n最後祝您在亂流下平安。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49c2b562290ea2f3410adb4d5416b0113a8dc94","tid":2345472,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"咁有冇用？"},{"pid":"7afd33f9204aaea4c60b724ec90c58ffa41d0d3e","tid":2345472,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9526d067cf3b0c4425f26c308d4739ac8e173795","tid":2345472,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d49c2b562290ea2f3410adb4d5416b0113a8dc94","tid":2345472,"uid":273627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"咁有冇用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"唔知喎 就好似占卜咁安心作用嚟"},{"pid":"b925c4e967ae75